/**
 * AUTO-VISUALS PROOFS (Phase 3, 2026-07-21) — the moment a SONG finishes, a
 * lyric video, an audio-reactive visualizer and 3-5 thumbnails are generated by
 * cheap ffmpeg/image EDITS off the EXISTING master audio + lyrics + cover, NEVER
 * a re-render, $0. This proves: the VERBATIM even-paced lyric paging (with the
 * HONEST "not karaoke sync" caveat), the thumbnail variant plan, the single-pass
 * argv construction (1080x1920 vertical + "afro" watermark), the fail-soft
 * batch, the auto-trigger wiring on song completion, and — when ffmpeg + the
 * Anton font are available — the real renders (ffprobe dims + audio + burned
 * watermark/lyrics on real pixels, real thumbnail images, partial batch survival).
 *
 * Offline by design (mirrors test-clips.ts): the CONSTRUCTION + PLANNER + SOURCE-
 * SCAN laws always run; the ffmpeg render legs run only when the binary answers,
 * and the drawtext legs additionally need the cached Anton font — each skip is
 * announced honestly, never a fake pass.
 */
